        {
          "field_name": "interest_calculation_method",
          "candidate_value": "What type of savings accounts does BMO offer? BMO offers several savings accounts, including: Savings Amplifier: Earn a competitive interest rate and get unlimited self-serve transfers with no monthly fees. You can earn a promotional interest rate * when you open a Savings Amplifier Account and a BMO chequing account. Premium Rate Savings: Open this account together with a BMO chequing account under the same plan. Earn daily interest on every dollar. Transaction fees vary depending on the plan you choose. U.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings: Open this account together with a BMO chequing account under the same plan. Save in U.S. dollars and earn interest. Transaction fees vary depending on the plan you choose. More questions? Can I add this savings account to Family Bundle? Sorry, but this savings account is not eligible for Family Bundle. Only Premium Rate Savings and U.S. Dollar Premium",
