          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What type of savings accounts does BMO offer?\nBMO offers several savings accounts, including:\nSavings Amplifier: Earn a competitive interest rate and get unlimited self-serve transfers with no monthly fees. You can earn a promotional\u00a0interest rate * when you open a Savings Amplifier Account and a BMO chequing account.\nPremium Rate Savings: Open this account together with a BMO chequing account under the same plan. Earn daily interest on every dollar. Transaction fees vary depending on the plan you choose.\nU.S. Dollar Premium Rate Savings: Open this account together with a BMO chequing account under the same plan. Save in U.S. dollars and earn interest. Transaction fees vary depending on the plan you choose.\nMore questions? Can I add this savings account to Family Bundle? Sorry, but this savings account is not eligible for Family Bundle. Only Premium Rate Savings and U.S. Dollar Premium",
